thread.title: Sonia
thread.title_full: Muscle Meals Direct reviewed by Sonia

author: Sonia
title: Sonia
text: I found it very easy to sign up and order, and had a prompt response to an online query. I had no trouble with picking up my order, but it's great that I can also get it delivered if the need arises. And really enjoying the meals! Very tasty, and a really convenient way for me to work on my weight goals.
